pageContext.claim: “We had 25 thousand people that wanted to be there [in Minnesota]....We had 25,000 people that wanted to go....Actually, had we had the rally, we would've had 25, 30,000 people there. Thousands and -- You probably saw it. Thousands of people showed up.”
pageContext.analysis: Media reports said "several hundred people" were waiting to see Trump. There is no evidence he would have attracted 25,000 people.
